    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strips of cloth, either plain or decorative, that cross the quilt top horizontally, vertically or diagonally, joining the quilt component blocks together.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
